# Golomb Ruler

<catsoop-section>Introduction</catsoop-section>

Unlike the regular ruler which has marks at each unit measure, the Golomb ruler is a specific type of ruler that has only a few integer markings. Inspired by the idea, this is a modified version of the original Golomb ruler.

<catsoop-section>Materials Required</catsoop-section>

- Golomb Rulers: 2

